margin: 24px 0 0; text-align: center; font-size: 32px;"&gt; 230亿欧元&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 8px;"&gt;西班牙已&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/06w8ejnynI5GxBcobqcTvA952PNs9cfIxQAlbrdqX6EhA_L4fo_ksXyuUmM2MeD413zHAI4JJN9UgdIiZFw83DNHyZJvJXUKFpAxfXkHHvSsZkdajcIJ3Dp7NIrm9tRljb7FTZxvuHM9WUR0nu7q5ccw42PGCWhqJp3sfukWNUijtI_ZQd7Aqs1GxAuZ3zNoq4qjzNqH3iIowTpKgKnXhv9tCAgopA3vJOF-k0zbnIKE_y7S3US3aDRhagDYgW88FZMAU6FparhZAmpDHgBSQcZPlNXtD_lb63o49QQeD2DtvSlJBdg_Jp3ZQ-rdwGyQ6Gz9_Ld7TgFAfezUJmzD_nmQPTRUuaEvSpFf2XMOwqx7G219g10_JZOar2aUtvPx90prl6KrJneqn46vWh90HYYcaSDXxczzbTpF0rES7nV954_sgVze-Ti45MiYPFc287R0SNb0jCU_Zy40cIQquexdZ3yxZhJFgyy9ISASolewPqVe1ONT39FbcFkdgrcoMyMpEXjOZAfSA1ovLTdXIDNnFImPdSsNFA/FrI3BcIJxY8QOr4lHKq_QhFEKbaabDTt/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="西班牙正在利用国防预算应对气候变化影响"&gt;承诺将大量国防开支用于救灾&lt;/a&gt;。随着气候变化恶化，一些军队可能越来越多地被要求应对极端天气及其影响。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;战争的持久遗产&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div style="margin-top: 24px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;"&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center; font-size: 22px; margin: 0;"&gt; “现在很痛苦，但这将对公共健康&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/tFjv4dN2UPhNwOplDmkXCDxM-A3MSA8rjhR-ywMtT9Dt0xbcvpcMm7xbPGmFHEdlU4qmSxpdatIOaaTe-ogvZmy-qn5l4w2H2F4tEDovNWILBz9uRLHwOGCaQ2GYNje9kC7QyayW-2sdserxvHfr0u7kj_QYV3MLyjwphEXq8Vy_n7beJjK0J5bFVvRZKz78WTfqAWPpC3KSn4grBtFm-WQRG2LHTlmFiqUUpUJ3Q1GzVHYp_qCwMN8B3VUUnR2nRK1V7VvNz0tAzgV4n640iEtQSew1RuRDBnotjrtlwfWZqNzcM3_cON_XD3SNGzvQx-lpdUZXRgtHWdFr-5qnAuqZ0A_NgU06pg_9H97IKxO-IzcRWOb5w_3O3Vpfv8hLKszAqYC1zuXrN8aD8NMh6fd1I84iVQu-xqEcot9WDttG2trIRegPu_RC1Lc26GAXk7VtTpjkOZTpkYO4x2tBGZp_C3F-BQ2hz1L9plm8yw/SbYi_yO1-gJ-E4LY8fAZws4jtOhWsiwA/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #00e; font-size: inherit;" target="_blank" title="加沙战争留下了垃圾、疾病和污染等有毒遗产"&gt;产生长期影响&lt;/a&gt;。”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p