t;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/p0dEjSYe-VXAoJ9B5svqEm5fk4U_CwMSyYJsJgfbIFMXj-QWyoj4KhKATTOhAHVwoIN-nrv05wnHU9Q8tsHfxDgEDgIPuons-Mqvo6qhEw9yQ8rTVGzHEZiVUEgWdq44JMJqjnYeQ1HHKv6Gg3sLxKECFb4YqPoLEOhvIOSZ3CIoEhnNf84YLjLAsdFbERWUCnhQ07iratF4rA90r1J9B5OMpVz_HL7bTBDZPD4gHtkXjMcE0HKF0MNRsC_CNHZAXaBfT2jcsl5nwzWe2Y-3W4oz7TaTLcjULn0f4GjCLWjFZCXhd7yq0lelAt_jbEF6mGuhnBaCElUV7bCN9YNQWhuvGQCXWFA9WDZCWOA0UDlge7TkaAUrxnvrbNNt2nbUcN971iMnxXnofLo-R_IrkTaZiCxgLe0U79zoTisW_30Ku7kw4T6kiOZwjtGjuKotwkNByaKwM0bHOaysmfp1k5cbDt_XvHWfaPE_cwCMjvYe7kMrF2UZakLCPbezDU-zQqYp/6d1k7COrG0yZHQTPuQ-lLoa0mWgnBIWu/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="随着人工智能、伊朗战争风险的增加，《豪七》进入调整期"&gt;陷入回调&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;大型科技公司的彭博指数收盘价比 10 月份的记录低 10% 以上，该技术水平表明存在调整。该指数继周四下跌 1.9%后，周五又下跌 1.6%，近几周盘中多次短暂跌破该水平，但尚未收于该水平。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/eMyoxmZSEE71nCcHt9up4fZODmr7Tq2ATauWaZSfeEAYA589HDlWrs5mVx-6RNQkR-dVBjhvVM-jxkBJcvU5sPyS73m69jIjLv7ZIxEoJXei-RQnjcapd_pDG_-A8R6vbmuOSooTdts6PkcJctfhQglcsNzIX89QfGPVISAelcXLq-pafLBm2OYKS-uTa9YTg0UaGuUjYd0dZSyQcBucQMIVtuFjySPSotj8meVY6ka4BnXxkkufPpqT3BuuCV3aiWprZEeZfbJmTldumJzizSdw5k8msIML7lSnSpvKfy_B08SxQ0qhDc1qLfDBqS4igc8f4_zzHHQDSGzbeSVHgltQOePTDo6infuoZN-U6RSSdfgihNug_gcMGwU3l91u3ziLOLSIcRDBlxDg8w/Wd5lzr_l7nAuo47SEWs5BWebU0r7Ej0v/18" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iKJrSg5ghpWo/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" alt="" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iKJrSg5ghpWo/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/figure&gt;&lt;div style="margin-top: 24px;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/DButDRC8UbOW4UnkEirF6ckkrISepFEDHOrkcESPgwnCXCuHuBBoujFbDkxVc9zM8GHZPrY3k8PekniccWFMMxDCzYvOPa7qV8hOD9ih1b7AG2zPZDVwkWLF8JZZSAHALfwqeoNmdcFNBE2SN6JahZujEGob5Nr3gnQqpltm2JdheQ1tfRNDwvXIu_mroHrUmgGldIyQcm5NGEMUdL1SzkIShmyK3hffOWSrsFej93LynTya4zKivBvRs7VAbBLVoVfeVEUH2c08KAJH7x8FIjGiSk8lV9ibFfyXK-4_5s1yc5VB864iCiQSqnLKiK2bsxH45-DPkK_edqN_M4b5E2oU3jyLgGplSrhDnPY0iIFsfmKCph2Ef3V6n1apufWdQPcrW7YODRYM563eWEw_CDz77Qw/6ZJ3pGy70cGGGjKOee0mSAXqQrkwDCXH/18" style="font-size: inherit; color: inherit; text-decoration: none;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: normal; margin: 12px 0 0 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;彭博播客&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="line-height: normal; font-weight: 700; margin: 12px 0 0 0; font-size: 20px !important;"&gt;对日常数字世界征税的呼声日益高涨&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="line-height: 1.4; margin: 12px 0 0 0; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px !important;"&gt;从在线银行和社交媒体到数字广告和人工智能订阅，数字服务是全球贸易中增长最快的部分。与实物出口不同，它们几乎不受监管、征税或关税。到目前为止。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style="display: block; width: 100%; height: 40px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; border: 1px solid; border-radius: 8px; margin: 16px 0 0 0; font-size: 14px !important;"&gt;阅读更多&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style="border-top: 1px solid; margin: 24px 0 0 0;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;随着一条重要天然气管道的修复&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;，秘鲁多年来最严重的国内能源危机&lt;/strong&gt;即将结束。但在重大泄漏迫使该国主要天然气田&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/Rb2ae4PuiGJBGLr4vtyg8xNKAGr3UDmBVp4FmnZpnvkSNniJxwLZi4AQvs61Hec3mnLJxM675-to351p75m6iptg5AUY9iw3Shkw_IItjy65jYIDH2SGEnKRVaAaCD08hLkGHeIWmJ7yk2FUXX1UhjssDhwazrCdAfv3mgpQfxRjnPIochTIeN1Ye8v14iDkBWS4CZj_yK1OuLl-_nUXK3SPJ2nePlZaltpfgXmmr6aktRcrz4T__8ODE-DWOhh4ETsNVTTx3cL2AfwjN-kAHCBUwlyZ1mcxXZRq6HrgL